coupon.additional_terms:
港幣$100現金券 Eye’sMate Optical
．此電子現金券只適用於愛視美眼鏡荷里活廣場分店；
．此電子現金券只適用於購買任何鏡架、鏡片、太陽眼鏡、非特價鏡架連鏡片 1 次消費滿港幣 $1200 或以上;
．此電子現金券不適用購買隱形眼鏡、特價品、眼科視光檢查、隱形眼鏡護理藥水、眼藥水和配件；
．請於開單前，出示此電子現金券作證明;
．此電子現金券不可以與其他優惠同時使用，不可累積使用；
．此電子現金券不可兌換現金及不作現金找贖；
．此電子現金券逾期無效；
．愛視美眼鏡保留修改以上優惠及細則之權利;
．如有任何爭議, 愛視美眼鏡將保留最終決定權;
．此電子現金券有效日期至2024 年 12 月 31 日。

Terms and Conditions
．The digital cash coupon is only suitable to Eye’s Mate Optical Diamond Hill branch
．The coupon is only suitable for the purchase of any frames, lenses, sunglasses, non-special offer frames and lenses on a single transaction of HKD$1,200 or above;
．The coupon is not suitable for purchasing contact lens, eye examination fee, optical accessories, eye health solution;
．Please present the digital cash coupon as proof when using the coupon ;
．The coupon cannot be used conjunction with other offers and cannot be used cumulatively;
．The coupon cannot be exchanged for cash and is not redeemable in cash;
．The coupon will be invalid if the coupon is expired;
．Eye’s Mate Optical reserves the right to alter or terminate the coupon and amend the terms and conditions at any time without notice;
．In case of any dispute, Eye’s Mate Optical reserves the right to make the final decision;
．The coupon is valid for 31 Dec 2024.

